<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/190/ayat/2/point/c> legal:hasText "pembatasan kegiatan usaha," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/190/ayat/2> legal:hasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/190/ayat/2/point/d> .
