<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/190/ayat/2/point/e> legal:hasText "pembatalan persetujuan:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/190/ayat/2> legal:hasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/190/ayat/2/point/f> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/190/ayat/2/point/f> legal:hasKey "f" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/190/ayat/2/point/f> legal:hasText "pembatalan pendaftaran," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/190/ayat/2> legal:hasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/190/ayat/2/point/g> .
