<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/190/ayat/2/point/g> legal:hasText "penghentian sementara sebagian atau seluruh alat produksi," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/190/ayat/2> legal:hasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/190/ayat/2/point/h> .
